snippet.title: Battlefront Plus V6 Trailer - UPDATE IS OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Get ready for the most weapons, abilities, characters, and appearances you've seen yet. Battlefront+ V6 releases TOMORROW (January 28th 2023)
Very special thanks to Hammie for creating this trailer! Consider supporting him and checking out his content: 
https://paypal.me/addisonshaw
https://www.nexusmods.com/users/80723208?tab=user+files

Check out the fully detailed breakdown of V6 in the Community Update here! https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vR33OnARgCzJ7ASglTFi_sI13HhZqZClp-PvdgDhpJa3OUv0c4kyuPmnvzlmxpUA7XBtng0HfF5YY2T/pub

Join our Discord to keep up to date on Battlefront Plus and hang out with the devs! https://discord.gg/99VtTgFBqq
Consider supporting me by donating to my Ko-fi! https://ko-fi.com/thespartancv

You can find Battlefront+ at the following link:
https://www.nexusmods.com/starwarsbattlefront22017/mods/7592
